classDiagram

class Owner {
    +name
    +pets
    +add_pet()
    +get_all_tasks()
}

class Pet {
    +name
    +species
    +tasks
    +add_task()
}

class Task {
    +description
    +time
    +frequency
    +completed
    +mark_complete()
}

class Scheduler {
    +sort_by_time()
    +filter_by_pet()
    +filter_by_status()
    +mark_task_complete()
    +detect_conflicts()
}

Owner "1" --> "*" Pet
Pet "1" --> "*" Task
Scheduler --> Owner     